$0.20 EPS Expected for Pointer Telocation Ltd (PNTR); CH Robinson Worldwide (CHRW) Shorts Raised By 5.31%


					
						July 26, 2017 - By Adrian Erickson


 Analysts expect Pointer Telocation Ltd (NASDAQ:PNTR) to report $0.20 EPS on August, 10.They anticipate $0.02 EPS change or 11.11% from last quarter’s $0.18 EPS. PNTR’s profit would be $1.60M giving it 17.20 P/E if the $0.20 EPS is correct. After having $0.29 EPS previously, Pointer Telocation Ltd’s analysts see -31.03% EPS growth. About 23,860 shares traded. Pointer Telocation Ltd (NASDAQ:PNTR) has risen 53.73% since July 26, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 37.03% the S&P500.







 CH Robinson Worldwide Incorporated (NASDAQ:CHRW) had an increase of 5.31% in short interest. CHRW’s SI was 16.69 million shares in July as released by FINRA. Its up 5.31% from 15.85M shares previously. With 1.19M avg volume, 14 days are for CH Robinson Worldwide Incorporated (NASDAQ:CHRW)’s short sellers to cover CHRW’s short positions. The SI to CH Robinson Worldwide Incorporated’s float is 11.87%. About 1.03 million shares traded. C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) has declined 7.85% since July 26, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 24.55% the S&P500.
C.H. Robinson Worldwide, Inc. is a provider of transportation services and logistics solutions through a network of offices operating in North America, Europe, Asia, Australia, New Zealand and South America. The company has market cap of $9.34 billion. The Company’s divisions include North American Surface Transportation , Global Forwarding, Robinson Fresh, and All Other and Corporate. It has a 19.36 P/E ratio. The NAST segment provides freight transportation services across North America through a network of offices in the United States, Canada and Mexico.
Among 21 analysts covering C.H. Robinson Worldwide (NASDAQ:CHRW), 5 have Buy rating, 6 Sell and 10 Hold. Therefore 24% are positive. C.H. Robinson Worldwide had 51 analyst reports since July 30, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. Raymond James downgraded C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) on Monday, July 18 to “Market Perform” rating. The stock has “Outperform” rating by Raymond James on Thursday, February 4. The rating was downgraded by UBS to “Sell” on Monday, July 11. Cowen & Co maintained the stock with “Hold” rating in Monday, July 10 report. As per Thursday, July 20, the company rating was maintained by Bank of America. The stock of C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) has “Market Perform” rating given on Wednesday, July 29 by Cowen & Co. As per Wednesday, August 19, the company rating was initiated by FinnCap. Bank of America downgraded C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) on Wednesday, December 2 to “Underperform” rating. Cowen & Co maintained C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) rating on Thursday, October 29. Cowen & Co has “Market Perform” rating and $71 target. The stock of C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) earned “Hold” rating by Zacks on Wednesday, August 26.
Since February 6, 2017, it had 0 buys, and 7 sales for $3.27 million activity. Freeman Angela K. also sold $94,535 worth of C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) on Friday, April 28. On Monday, February 6 WIEHOFF JOHN sold $1.83 million worth of C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) or 24,306 shares. Campbell Ben G had sold 4,865 shares worth $389,784. Another trade for 3,500 shares valued at $281,066 was made by LINDBLOOM CHAD on Tuesday, February 28. Another trade for 1,079 shares valued at $83,774 was sold by Biesterfeld Robert C Jr. OBRIEN CHRIS also sold $200,435 worth of C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) on Wednesday, February 8. On Tuesday, February 28 the insider LEMKE JAMES sold $388,169.
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.78 in 2016 Q4. Its down 0.30, from 1.08 in 2016Q3. It turned negative, as 43 investors sold C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc shares while 191 reduced holdings. 52 funds opened positions while 131 raised stakes. 122.38 million shares or 4.77% more from 116.81 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Korea Inv accumulated 44,168 shares. Moreover, Meiji Yasuda Asset Management Com Ltd has 0.11% invested in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) for 12,864 shares. Moreover, Ironwood Investment Counsel Limited Liability Com has 0.93% invested in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW). Jacobs Levy Equity Mngmt holds 0.28% or 198,700 shares. Moreover, Suntrust Banks Inc has 0% invested in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW). Advantus Cap Mngmt reported 13,973 shares. Huntington State Bank accumulated 5,100 shares. Rodgers Brothers reported 0.24% in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW). Vision invested 1.38% in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW). Wells Fargo And Mn holds 0.01% in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW) or 452,754 shares. The Ontario – Canada-based Sun Life Inc has invested 0% in C.H. Robinson Worldwide Inc (NASDAQ:CHRW). Cambridge Invest Rech Advsr invested in 0.45% or 326,199 shares. Gulf International Bank (Uk) owns 42,636 shares. Schwab Charles Inv Mgmt holds 648,365 shares or 0.05% of its portfolio. Seizert Partners Ltd Liability holds 2.09% or 802,111 shares in its portfolio.








