Pointer Telocation

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Pointer Telocation Ltd.)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Pointer Telocation Ltd.


Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: PNTR


Predecessor
Nexus Telocation Systems Ltd.


