                About Pointer            


Optimize Your Mobile Resources

Optimizing operations is the most efficient way to increase your profitability. Without adding another vehicle, cargo haul or new driver you’ll be able to boost profitability by improving your fleet’s performance. Pointer provides you with a range of tools, technologies and services that optimize your fleet’s performance. Moreover, the valuable insights you’ll have via our advanced analytics allow your organization to continually improve every aspect of your operations.        







Here's What You Need





 Increased Operational Efficiency



 Enhanced Safety & Compliance



 Comprehensive Asset Security



 Effective Fraud Mitigation










What Makes the Difference
Tailor-made solutions fortified by ongoing analysis and guidance for continual improvement. We’re your partners, not simply solution providers. Together, we’ll ensure your increased performance, productivity and profitability in real time and over time.






